的，以及如何使用多重技巧质证证人证言及物证的真实性、确定性，以达致辩方辩护策略与目的；</span></p></li><li><p style="margin: 0px 8px 15px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.5em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">中美尖峰对话：中美律师调查取证权作用与实践比较，兼谈306条职业风险、中美刑事诉讼证据开示制度比较及国内适用；美国的辩诉交易与中国的认罪认罚从宽制度的实践与对比。</span></p></li></ul><p style="margin: 5px 1em;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(49, 102, 140)"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 5px 1em;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">在这里，</span></span></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 5px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-size: 14px;">获得一次技巧突飞猛进的稀缺机会，</span><br/></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 5px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(7