dding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">美国专家在精心设计的案例中通过模拟审判的方式，向中国律师讲解交叉询问的逻辑结构及其目的，以及如何使用多重技巧质证证人证言以及物证的真实性、确定性，以达致辩方辩护策略与目的。在庭审辩论技巧之外，美方专家还将讲解美国法律制度中刑事辩护律师应当遵守的职业道德以及法律。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px 15px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.5em"><strong style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">本次课程核心内容包括：</span><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;color: rgb(71, 71, 71);font-size: 15px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><ul style="list-style-type: circle;padding-left:30px;" class=" list-paddingleft-2"><li><p style="margin: 0px 8px 15px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.5em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">中国非法证据排除、交叉询问的发展及趋势；</span></p></li><li><p style="margin: 0px 8px 15px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.5em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">律师接受案件后如何着手以及准备辩护策略；</span></p></li><li><p style="margin: 0px 8px 15px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;line-height: 1.5em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !