8、麦克·约翰逊、菲利普·普罗、玛丽·巴尔：交叉询问的作用及其重要性

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appO83kdBt04848/v_5c9884d4a8aee_guM1wHoj

<p style="margin: 25px 1em;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em"><strong style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-size: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(49, 102, 140); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">麦克·约翰逊（Michael Johnson）</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(71, 71, 71); font-size: 15px;">，美国前总统克林顿“白水门案”（Whitewater Case）主控检察官，曾在美国联邦司法部任职十年以上，做过美国联邦检察官，执业经验近四十年。</span><br/></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">2017年3月，他主持并参与了在美国西雅图举办的</span><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">针对中国大法官和资深检察官的有关以庭审为中心的专业技能培训</span><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">，参与者对培训做了高度评价。自2010年以来，其专注培训执业律师的庭审技巧，是美国著名的律师培训机构全国庭审技巧研究院（National
 Institute of Trial 
Advocacy）首席导师。主持和参加过很多国际培训项目，包括苏格兰、爱尔兰、利比里亚以及南非等国家的律师培训。</span></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">那么，庭审实质化背景下，美国法庭的交叉询问技巧对于国内的刑辩律师有哪些启发？为何中国的法官、检察官也必须去参与其培训呢？</span></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">亲身参与过、体验过，经历过中美法庭庭审技能培训的刑辩大咖们如是说：</span></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important"><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 0px none"><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 0px none"><section style="margin: 5px 2px;padding: 20px 10px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 1px dashed rgb(220, 216, 217);box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 4px"><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnYxZDjnz1500/image/ueditor/88531600_1514539745.cn/mmbiz_png/eujcwj5gxvickyjv2jvmo4skcsfkcia6axbib6bvzfb6vsoficoyxcbeibooc2rgc6bibeepfrgiavdl1atzcvpwsizew/640" style=";padding: 0px;height: auto !important;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: auto !important;visibility: visible !important"/></p><p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153)">虽然中美法系不同，刑辩技能却有共性。这种头脑风暴式的深度参与的强化训练，会让大家体验到法庭质证和辩论的真正风采，而且这种训练正是律师最需要的。</span></p><p style="margin: 5px 0px 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: right;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153)">——田文昌谈中美法庭庭审技能培训</span></p></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 5px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em"><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important"><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 0px none"><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 0px none"><section style="margin: 5px 2px;padding: 20px 10px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 1px dashed rgb(220, 216, 217);box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 4px"><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnYxZDjnz1500/image/ueditor/2145400_1514539746.cn/mmbiz_png/eujcwj5gxvickyjv2jvmo4skcsfkcia6axmm8lxcqwpc6aujkcmlupegkqlh4qgh5ib6vkplgvxuoywbgqbyeibc3g/640" style=";padding: 0px;height: auto !important;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: 421px;visibility: visible !important"/></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153)">有人说“交叉询问”是“屠龙术”，没有用。其实，还是有用的，我们目前的法庭发问、讯问，并没有做好。未来，中国刑事诉讼制度，最终要走向与国际刑事司法准则接轨。为今天和明天同时准备吧！</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: right;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153)">——毛立新谈中美法庭庭审技能培训</span></p></section><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: 0px;height: 0px;clear: both"></section></section><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal"><br/></p></section></section><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important"><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 0px none"><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 0px none"><section style="margin: 5px 2px;padding: 20px 10px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 1px dashed rgb(220, 216, 217);box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 4px"><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnYxZDjnz1500/image/ueditor/34118500_1514539746.cn/mmbiz_jpg/eujcwj5gxvickyjv2jvmo4skcsfkcia6axwct3lickszs5pnntvibi31b6j0cou9wu5u4qwjktyk7m3ypc6vdw8qeg/640" style=";padding: 0px;height: auto !important;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: auto !important;visibility: visible !important"/></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153)">作为诉讼律师，什么都可以不懂，但是必须要懂得发问，懂得在庭上问问题。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 1em;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;letter-spacing: 1px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: right"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153)">——香港大律师张耀良谈交叉询问重要性</span></p></section><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: 0px;height: 0px;clear: both"></section></section><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal"><br/></p></section></section><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important"><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 0px none"><section style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 0px none"><section style="margin: 5px 2px;padding: 20px 10px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;border: 1px dashed rgb(220, 216, 217);box-shadow: rgb(200, 200, 200) 0px 0px 4px"><p style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appnYxZDjnz1500/image/ueditor/48479000_1514539746.cn/mmbiz_png/eujcwj5gxvickyjv2jvmo4skcsfkcia6axtwbhlhmh3hk5oxrgiaicwibbn1yqdjbt7swvgbc0jdzvqtibuuw9thw0ug/640" style=";padding: 0px;height: auto !important;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: auto !important;visibility: visible !important"/></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153)">刑事辩护作为一个重要的法治和保障人权的制度性设计，是需要不断创新及提升的，美国经验当然适用中国。</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 1em 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: right;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153)">——虞平谈中美法庭庭审技能培训</span></p></section></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">从</span><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">以上观点中，以庭审为中心的大势下，更强调律师的专业度，作为诉讼律师，必须要懂得发问，懂得如何在庭上问问题以达到最佳辩护效果，而这种训练正是律师最需要的。这次</span></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em 5px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170)">不需要远赴重洋，跋山涉水；</span></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em 5px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170)">不需要动辄数万的交通费用；</span></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em 5px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170)">不存在语言障碍，无法沟通；</span></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em 5px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170)">不存在中美隔阂，难以本土化……</span></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em 5px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170)">这一切，抱柱将一一为你搞定！</span></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em 5px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170)">我们将美国专家们搬到眼前，</span></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em"><strong style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">麦克·约翰逊教授携美国联邦法院前院长及美国资深刑辩律师特意为中国律师设计了一场专门的国际级庭审技能实战训练！</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em"><span style=";padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(71, 71, 71)">而为了让本次课程的价值最大化，主办方更是邀请了数十位国内顶级法律大咖，共同参与其中，从中国律师的角度出发对美国导师的观点进行解读与实操讲解！</span></p><p style="margin: 25px 1em 5px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 1px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em"><sp